  "id": "RAW_a095fa7a",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-11-28）：DeepSeek-Math-V2 开源，以 LLM 验证器实现自验证，攻克数学推理严谨性难题",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500644&idx=1&sn=ea3f14f6ce7da3eba0573c28207b039c",
  "date": "2025-11-28 09:18:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：DeepSeek-Math-V2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"384\" data-imgfileid=\"100016983\" data-ratio=\"0.3296296296296296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=188ce703&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwrQicaRCG3nG4VhTVhF8DVhcOhWMljwU3ZT5C2IkkaIhq1siay58JF2wRcQ7ZkI4RI4VTyTpOecLMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DeepSeek-Math-V2 是一个旨在实现自验证数学推理的大型语言模型。通过强化学习奖励正确的最终答案，该模型在数学推理方面取得了显著进展。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">然而，正确答案并不总能保证正确的推理，尤其是在需要逐步推导的定理证明任务中。DeepSeek-Math-V2 通过训练一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">基于 LLM 的验证器</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来验证推理的全面性和严谨性，并使用验证器作为奖励模型来训练证明生成器。该模型在多个数学竞赛中表现出色，表明自验证数学推理是一个可行的研究方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepseek-math-v2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepseek-math-v2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：DifficultySampling</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"650\" data-imgfileid=\"100016979\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=696bd8ae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwrQicaRCG3nG4VhTVhF8DVhXOxg2uib6dja65HrVHYzLygSib1wxFRhtkoTibF7prIcM8uu8Eq8en7hw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DifficultySampling项目深入研究了多模态后训练中的难度感知数据采样，旨在优化多模态推理和感知能力，而无需依赖监督微调。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目探讨了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">难度感知采样</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">在数学推理、视觉感知、图表解读等多模态任务中的应用潜力，并评估了其在不同任务类型中的具体改进效果。项目还提出了一种适用于不同规模和基线能力的多模态大语言模型的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">难度区分框架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/difficultysampling\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/difficultysampling</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Awesome Nano Banana Pro</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"398\" data-imgfileid=\"100016977\" data-ratio=\"0.3425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=afd1ed1b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwrQicaRCG3nG4VhTVhF8DVhqmORNvsDrZfao20NGichzRf6MFYnZExZsh5DJqPic5Ria1bjcUkfL6pfw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Awesome Nano Banana Pro 是一个精心策划的资源集合，专注于 Nano Banana pro（Nano banana 2）AI 图像模型的提示工程和创意潜力探索。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">高保真</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的图像生成提示，适用于从照片写实到风格化美学以及复杂的创意实验。资源来源包括 X（Twitter）、微信、Replicate 和顶级提示工程师，旨在帮助用户充分发挥模型的潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/awesome-nanobanana-pro2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/awesome-nanobanana-pro2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：UDA_Debias</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"354\" data-imgfileid=\"100016975\" data-ratio=\"0.3037037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=51eeed49&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwrQicaRCG3nG4VhTVhF8DVhibN74GkTgE5sic3Z5dZAERdqiaXycbCokvksjIX2ibJDh5zgtTfxe6ACxQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UDA_Debias项目旨在解决大型语言模型（LLMs）对比评估中的偏好偏差问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">传统的对比评估容易受到评审者偏好的影响，导致不一致和偏斜的排名。UDA（无监督去偏对齐）框架通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">动态调整Elo评分系统</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来减少评审者之间的分歧。该框架使用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">紧凑的神经网络</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">自适应地设置K因子并优化胜率概率，完全在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">无监督</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的情况下运行，以</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">最小化所有评审者Elo轨迹的离散度</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">为目标，从而实现</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">更稳定和可重复</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的评估。实验表明，UDA显著降低了评审者间评分标准差，并提高了与人类判断的平均相关性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uda-debias\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uda-debias</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：Wave Terminal</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"326\" data-imgfileid=\"100016973\" data-ratio=\"0.2814814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7658561d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwrQicaRCG3nG4VhTVhF8DVhbtIdXmo7UeMME3IjBlugLyurulfpicWQAWherkv0uBHaqlMmRKutuicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Wave Terminal 是一个开源的跨平台终端，结合了传统终端功能与图形化能力，如文件预览、网页浏览和 AI 辅助。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它支持 MacOS、Linux 和 Windows 系统，旨在将图形工具直接引入终端，用户可以在命令行中控制这些工具，从而在保持终端工作流的同时，访问所需的可视化界面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/waveterm\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/waveterm</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Acontext</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"218\" data-imgfileid=\"100016971\" data-ratio=\"0.18703703703703703\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5092270c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwrQicaRCG3nG4VhTVhF8DVhDqGMnNgAUPIHw8iaCZ2afU5KSuShXLnQJ331QbY5sxAfDiaLbfJ55eNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Acontext是一个专为自学习Agent设计的上下文数据平台，旨在简化上下文工程，提高Agent的可靠性和任务成功率。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该平台通过存储上下文和工件、观察Agent任务和用户反馈，帮助Agent进行自我学习。Acontext提供本地仪表板以查看消息、任务、工件和经验，支持多模态会话和任务Agent，帮助构建更具可扩展性的Agent产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/acontext\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/acontext</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
